  user_input {
    user_response: "# ALUMNIIQ \342\200\224 AI POWERED ALUMNI CAREER INTELLIGENCE PLATFORM\n\nYou are a Senior Software Architect, Senior Product Designer, Senior UI/UX Designer, Senior React Engineer, Senior Flask Engineer, and AI Engineer.\n\nBuild a production-ready SaaS platform called:\n\n# AlumniIQ\n\nAn AI-powered Alumni Career Intelligence Platform that helps students, universities, researchers, and career centers discover alumni career paths through conversational AI and interactive analytics.\n\nThe product must feel comparable to:\n\n* ChatGPT\n* Claude\n* Perplexity\n* Linear\n* Stripe\n* Arc Browser\n\nThis must NOT feel like a student project.\n\n---\n\n# TECH STACK\n\nFrontend\n\n* React 19\n* TypeScript\n* Vite\n* Tailwind CSS\n* shadcn/ui\n* Lucide React\n* Framer Motion\n* React Router\n* Zustand\n* TanStack Query\n* React Markdown\n\nBackend\n\n* Python Flask\n* SQLAlchemy\n* Flask Blueprints\n* PostgreSQL\n* JWT Authentication\n\nAI\n\n* OpenAI Assistant API\n* Streaming Responses\n* Conversation History\n\nCharts\n\n* Recharts\n\nDeployment\n\n* Docker\n* Docker Compose\n* Environment Variables\n\n---\n\n# DESIGN PHILOSOPHY\n\nThe application should blend:\n\n* OpenAI\n* Linear\n* Stripe\n* Apple\n* Claude\n\nVisual Style:\n\n* Ultra Premium\n* Dark Mode First\n* Glassmorphism\n* Liquid Glass\n* Cinematic Motion\n* Large Typography\n* High-End SaaS Feel\n\nBackground:\n\n#000000\n\nCards:\n\nrgba(255,255,255,0.03)\n\nBorders:\n\nrgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n\nTypography:\n\nInstrument Serif\nInter\n\n---\n\n# FONT\n\nImport in index.css:\n\n@import url(\'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap\');\n\n---\n\n# LIQUID GLASS SYSTEM\n\nCreate reusable component class:\n\n.liquid-glass {\nbackground: rgba(255,255,255,0.01);\nbackground-blend-mode: luminosity;\nbackdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\nborder: none;\nbox-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\nposition: relative;\noverflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.liquid-glass::before {\ncontent: \"\";\nposition: absolute;\ninset: 0;\nborder-radius: inherit;\npadding: 1.4px;\n\nbackground: linear-gradient(\n180deg,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.45) 0%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.15) 20%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0) 40%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0) 60%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.15) 80%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.45) 100%\n);\n\n-webkit-mask:\nlinear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box,\nlinear-gradient(#fff 0 0);\n\n-webkit-mask-composite: xor;\nmask-composite: exclude;\n\npointer-events: none;\n}\n\nApply this style consistently across:\n\n* Navbar\n* Cards\n* Inputs\n* Buttons\n* Dashboard Widgets\n* Login Forms\n* Chat Interface\n\n---\n\n# APPLICATION FLOW\n\nPublic\n\nLanding Page\n\342\206\222 Login/Register\n\342\206\222 Dashboard\n\nAuthenticated\n\nDashboard\n\342\206\222 AI Assistant\n\342\206\222 Alumni Explorer\n\342\206\222 Career Insights\n\342\206\222 Profile\n\342\206\222 Settings\n\n---\n\n# ROUTES\n\nPublic\n\n/\nLanding Page\n\n/login\nLogin\n\n/register\nRegister\n\n/forgot-password\n\nProtected\n\n/dashboard\n\n/assistant\n\n/alumni\n\n/insights\n\n/profile\n\n/settings\n\n---\n\n# LANDING PAGE\n\nThe landing page must use cinematic videos and premium SaaS storytelling.\n\nAll sections must use Framer Motion reveal animations.\n\nAll content sits on bg-black.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 1 \342\200\224 HERO\n\nFull viewport.\n\nBackground Video:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260405_074625_a81f018a-956b-43fb-9aee-4d1508e30e6a.mp4\n\nImplement smooth fade loop:\n\n* Fade in on canplay\n* Fade out before ending\n* Restart\n* Fade back in\n\nNo CSS transition.\n\nUse requestAnimationFrame.\n\nNavbar:\n\nLogo:\nAlumniIQ\n\nLinks:\n\nFeatures\nExplorer\nInsights\nAbout\n\nButtons:\n\nLogin\nGet Started\n\nHero Content:\n\nHeading:\n\nDiscover where alumni become extraordinary.\n\nInstrument Serif\n\nLarge typography:\n\ntext-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl\n\nSubtitle:\n\nExplore alumni careers, uncover industry trends, and ask AI-powered questions about your university network.\n\nCTA:\n\nGet Started\n\nWatch Demo\n\nEmail capture field\n\nSocial icons:\n\nInstagram\nTwitter\nGlobe\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 2 \342\200\224 ABOUT ALUMNIIQ\n\nAnimated reveal.\n\nHeadline:\n\nTransform alumni data into career intelligence.\n\nBody:\n\nEvery graduate leaves a story behind.\n\nAlumniIQ transforms alumni records into actionable insights through AI-powered exploration, helping students understand career pathways, industry trends, and opportunities across the world.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 3 \342\200\224 AI DISCOVERY\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260402_054547_9875cfc5-155a-4229-8ec8-b7ba7125cbf8.mp4\n\nGlass card overlay.\n\nTitle:\n\nAI-Powered Alumni Discovery\n\nText:\n\nAsk questions naturally and receive instant insights from alumni data.\n\nExamples:\n\n* Which alumni work at Google?\n* Show alumni in Germany.\n* Top skills in Data Science.\n* Career paths in AI.\n\nButton:\n\nExplore AI Assistant\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 4 \342\200\224 CAREER INTELLIGENCE \303\227 HUMAN POTENTIAL\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260307_083826_e938b29f-a43a-41ec-a153-3d4730578ab8.mp4\n\nHeadline:\n\nCareer Intelligence \303\227 Human Potential\n\nBlock 1\n\nTitle:\n\nDiscover Patterns\n\nDescription:\n\nAnalyze career trajectories across countries, industries, and companies.\n\nBlock 2\n\nTitle:\n\nMake Better Decisions\n\nDescription:\n\nUse real alumni outcomes to guide education and career planning.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 5 \342\200\224 PRODUCT FEATURES\n\nTwo animated cards.\n\nCard 1\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260314_131748_f2ca2a28-fed7-44c8-b9a9-bd9acdd5ec31.mp4\n\nTag:\n\nAI Assistant\n\nTitle:\n\nAsk AlumniIQ\n\nDescription:\n\nReceive intelligent answers using OpenAI Assistant API and alumni knowledge.\n\n---\n\nCard 2\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260324_151826_c7218672-6e92-402c-9e45-f1e0f454bdc4.mp4\n\nTag:\n\nAnalytics\n\nTitle:\n\nCareer Intelligence Dashboard\n\nDescription:\n\nVisualize skills, industries, countries, and employers through interactive analytics.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 6 \342\200\224 ALUMNI EXPLORER SHOWCASE\n\nLarge product mockup.\n\nHeadline:\n\nExplore Thousands of Alumni Profiles\n\nFeatures:\n\n\342\234\223 Company Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Country Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Industry Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Skill Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Advanced Search\n\nDisplay realistic alumni cards.\n\nCard fields:\n\n* Name\n* Position\n* Company\n* Country\n* Education\n* Skills\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 7 \342\200\224 CAREER INSIGHTS SHOWCASE\n\nInteractive dashboard preview.\n\nHeadline:\n\nUnderstand Career Trends at Scale\n\nWidgets:\n\nTop Industries\n\nTop Countries\n\nTop Employers\n\nTop Skills\n\nCareer Growth Trends\n\nAnimated counters.\n\nGlass dashboard design.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 8 \342\200\224 PLATFORM PREVIEW\n\nSplit-screen layout.\n\nLeft:\n\nAI Assistant\n\nRight:\n\nCareer Dashboard\n\nHeadline:\n\nOne Platform.\nUnlimited Alumni Intelligence.\n\nButtons:\n\nGet Started\n\nLogin\n\n---\n\n# LOGIN PAGE\n\nUse same design language as landing page.\n\nBackground:\n\nUse Hero Video\n\nDark overlay:\n\nbg-black/60\n\nCentered liquid-glass card.\n\nTitle:\n\nWelcome Back\n\nSubtitle:\n\nAccess the Alumni Career Intelligence Platform\n\nFields:\n\nEmail\n\nPassword\n\nRemember Me\n\nForgot Password\n\nButtons:\n\nSign In\n\nContinue with Google\n\nContinue with Microsoft\n\nDesktop Right Side:\n\nAnimated feature cards:\n\nAI Assistant\n\nAlumni Explorer\n\nCareer Insights\n\nSmooth floating animations.\n\n---\n\n# REGISTER PAGE\n\nFields:\n\nFull Name\n\nEmail\n\nUniversity\n\nPassword\n\nConfirm Password\n\nButton:\n\nCreate Account\n\nSocial Login:\n\nGoogle\n\nMicrosoft\n\n---\n\n# DASHBOARD\n\nModern SaaS dashboard.\n\nWelcome section.\n\nStatistics cards:\n\nTotal Alumni\n\nCompanies\n\nCountries\n\nIndustries\n\nSuggested Questions:\n\n* Which alumni work in Google?\n* Show alumni in Germany.\n* Top AI professionals.\n* Most common alumni skills.\n\nQuick Actions:\n\nAsk AI\n\nExplore Alumni\n\nView Insights\n\n---\n\n# AI ASSISTANT\n\nInspired by ChatGPT + Claude.\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Streaming Responses\n* Markdown Rendering\n* Code Blocks\n* Copy Response\n* Typing Animation\n* Suggested Prompts\n* Conversation History\n* Source References\n\nLayout:\n\nSidebar\n\nChat Area\n\nPrompt Input\n\n---\n\n# ALUMNI EXPLORER\n\nSearch\n\nFilter\n\nSort\n\nPagination\n\nGrid/List Toggle\n\nAlumni Card:\n\nPhoto\n\nName\n\nPosition\n\nCompany\n\nCountry\n\nEducation\n\nSkills\n\nLinkedIn Button\n\nProfile Modal\n\n---\n\n# CAREER INSIGHTS\n\nInteractive Charts.\n\nUse Recharts.\n\nShow:\n\nTop Skills\n\nTop Industries\n\nTop Countries\n\nTop Companies\n\nCareer Progression Trends\n\nAnimated Loading States.\n\n---\n\n# SIDEBAR\n\nInspired by Linear.\n\nSections:\n\nDashboard\n\nAI Assistant\n\nAlumni Explorer\n\nCareer Insights\n\nProfile\n\nSettings\n\nLogout\n\nCollapsible.\n\nMobile Drawer.\n\n---\n\n# STATE MANAGEMENT\n\nUse Zustand.\n\nStores:\n\nauthStore\n\nchatStore\n\nalumniStore\n\nanalyticsStore\n\nthemeStore\n\n---\n\n# API SERVICES\n\n/services\n\nauthService.ts\n\nassistantService.ts\n\nalumniService.ts\n\nanalyticsService.ts\n\n---\n\n# BACKEND STRUCTURE\n\nbackend/\n\napp/\n\napi/\n\nauth/\n\nassistant/\n\nalumni/\n\nanalytics/\n\nmodels/\n\nservices/\n\nconfig/\n\nutils/\n\nDatabase Models:\n\nUser\n\nAlumni\n\nCompany\n\nCountry\n\nIndustry\n\nChatHistory\n\n---\n\n# API ENDPOINTS\n\nPOST /api/auth/login\n\nPOST /api/auth/register\n\nPOST /api/auth/logout\n\nGET /api/alumni\n\nGET /api/alumni/search\n\nGET /api/alumni/:id\n\nGET /api/analytics\n\nPOST /api/assistant/chat\n\nGET /api/chat/history\n\n---\n\n# AI INTEGRATION\n\nOpenAI Assistant API\n\nCapabilities:\n\n* Alumni Search\n* Career Discovery\n* Industry Analysis\n* Skill Insights\n* Career Recommendations\n\nSupport:\n\nStreaming Responses\n\nConversation Memory\n\nSource Citations\n\n---\n\n# CODE QUALITY\n\nRequirements:\n\n* TypeScript Strict Mode\n* Reusable Components\n* SOLID Principles\n* Clean Architecture\n* Responsive Design\n* Accessibility Support\n* Loading Skeletons\n* Empty States\n* Error Boundaries\n* Production Ready\n\nGenerate the complete application including:\n\n* Folder Structure\n* Frontend\n* Backend\n* Authentication\n* Landing Page\n* Login/Register\n* Dashboard\n* AI Assistant\n* Alumni Explorer\n* Career Insights\n* API Layer\n* Zustand Stores\n* Responsive Design\n* OpenAI Integration\n* Flask Integration\n* Modern SaaS UI\n* All Components\n* All Pages\n* Production-Ready Architecture\n"
    items {
      text: "# ALUMNIIQ \342\200\224 AI POWERED ALUMNI CAREER INTELLIGENCE PLATFORM\n\nYou are a Senior Software Architect, Senior Product Designer, Senior UI/UX Designer, Senior React Engineer, Senior Flask Engineer, and AI Engineer.\n\nBuild a production-ready SaaS platform called:\n\n# AlumniIQ\n\nAn AI-powered Alumni Career Intelligence Platform that helps students, universities, researchers, and career centers discover alumni career paths through conversational AI and interactive analytics.\n\nThe product must feel comparable to:\n\n* ChatGPT\n* Claude\n* Perplexity\n* Linear\n* Stripe\n* Arc Browser\n\nThis must NOT feel like a student project.\n\n---\n\n# TECH STACK\n\nFrontend\n\n* React 19\n* TypeScript\n* Vite\n* Tailwind CSS\n* shadcn/ui\n* Lucide React\n* Framer Motion\n* React Router\n* Zustand\n* TanStack Query\n* React Markdown\n\nBackend\n\n* Python Flask\n* SQLAlchemy\n* Flask Blueprints\n* PostgreSQL\n* JWT Authentication\n\nAI\n\n* OpenAI Assistant API\n* Streaming Responses\n* Conversation History\n\nCharts\n\n* Recharts\n\nDeployment\n\n* Docker\n* Docker Compose\n* Environment Variables\n\n---\n\n# DESIGN PHILOSOPHY\n\nThe application should blend:\n\n* OpenAI\n* Linear\n* Stripe\n* Apple\n* Claude\n\nVisual Style:\n\n* Ultra Premium\n* Dark Mode First\n* Glassmorphism\n* Liquid Glass\n* Cinematic Motion\n* Large Typography\n* High-End SaaS Feel\n\nBackground:\n\n#000000\n\nCards:\n\nrgba(255,255,255,0.03)\n\nBorders:\n\nrgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n\nTypography:\n\nInstrument Serif\nInter\n\n---\n\n# FONT\n\nImport in index.css:\n\n@import url(\'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap\');\n\n---\n\n# LIQUID GLASS SYSTEM\n\nCreate reusable component class:\n\n.liquid-glass {\nbackground: rgba(255,255,255,0.01);\nbackground-blend-mode: luminosity;\nbackdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\nborder: none;\nbox-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\nposition: relative;\noverflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.liquid-glass::before {\ncontent: \"\";\nposition: absolute;\ninset: 0;\nborder-radius: inherit;\npadding: 1.4px;\n\nbackground: linear-gradient(\n180deg,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.45) 0%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.15) 20%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0) 40%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0) 60%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.15) 80%,\nrgba(255,255,255,0.45) 100%\n);\n\n-webkit-mask:\nlinear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box,\nlinear-gradient(#fff 0 0);\n\n-webkit-mask-composite: xor;\nmask-composite: exclude;\n\npointer-events: none;\n}\n\nApply this style consistently across:\n\n* Navbar\n* Cards\n* Inputs\n* Buttons\n* Dashboard Widgets\n* Login Forms\n* Chat Interface\n\n---\n\n# APPLICATION FLOW\n\nPublic\n\nLanding Page\n\342\206\222 Login/Register\n\342\206\222 Dashboard\n\nAuthenticated\n\nDashboard\n\342\206\222 AI Assistant\n\342\206\222 Alumni Explorer\n\342\206\222 Career Insights\n\342\206\222 Profile\n\342\206\222 Settings\n\n---\n\n# ROUTES\n\nPublic\n\n/\nLanding Page\n\n/login\nLogin\n\n/register\nRegister\n\n/forgot-password\n\nProtected\n\n/dashboard\n\n/assistant\n\n/alumni\n\n/insights\n\n/profile\n\n/settings\n\n---\n\n# LANDING PAGE\n\nThe landing page must use cinematic videos and premium SaaS storytelling.\n\nAll sections must use Framer Motion reveal animations.\n\nAll content sits on bg-black.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 1 \342\200\224 HERO\n\nFull viewport.\n\nBackground Video:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260405_074625_a81f018a-956b-43fb-9aee-4d1508e30e6a.mp4\n\nImplement smooth fade loop:\n\n* Fade in on canplay\n* Fade out before ending\n* Restart\n* Fade back in\n\nNo CSS transition.\n\nUse requestAnimationFrame.\n\nNavbar:\n\nLogo:\nAlumniIQ\n\nLinks:\n\nFeatures\nExplorer\nInsights\nAbout\n\nButtons:\n\nLogin\nGet Started\n\nHero Content:\n\nHeading:\n\nDiscover where alumni become extraordinary.\n\nInstrument Serif\n\nLarge typography:\n\ntext-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl\n\nSubtitle:\n\nExplore alumni careers, uncover industry trends, and ask AI-powered questions about your university network.\n\nCTA:\n\nGet Started\n\nWatch Demo\n\nEmail capture field\n\nSocial icons:\n\nInstagram\nTwitter\nGlobe\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 2 \342\200\224 ABOUT ALUMNIIQ\n\nAnimated reveal.\n\nHeadline:\n\nTransform alumni data into career intelligence.\n\nBody:\n\nEvery graduate leaves a story behind.\n\nAlumniIQ transforms alumni records into actionable insights through AI-powered exploration, helping students understand career pathways, industry trends, and opportunities across the world.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 3 \342\200\224 AI DISCOVERY\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260402_054547_9875cfc5-155a-4229-8ec8-b7ba7125cbf8.mp4\n\nGlass card overlay.\n\nTitle:\n\nAI-Powered Alumni Discovery\n\nText:\n\nAsk questions naturally and receive instant insights from alumni data.\n\nExamples:\n\n* Which alumni work at Google?\n* Show alumni in Germany.\n* Top skills in Data Science.\n* Career paths in AI.\n\nButton:\n\nExplore AI Assistant\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 4 \342\200\224 CAREER INTELLIGENCE \303\227 HUMAN POTENTIAL\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260307_083826_e938b29f-a43a-41ec-a153-3d4730578ab8.mp4\n\nHeadline:\n\nCareer Intelligence \303\227 Human Potential\n\nBlock 1\n\nTitle:\n\nDiscover Patterns\n\nDescription:\n\nAnalyze career trajectories across countries, industries, and companies.\n\nBlock 2\n\nTitle:\n\nMake Better Decisions\n\nDescription:\n\nUse real alumni outcomes to guide education and career planning.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 5 \342\200\224 PRODUCT FEATURES\n\nTwo animated cards.\n\nCard 1\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260314_131748_f2ca2a28-fed7-44c8-b9a9-bd9acdd5ec31.mp4\n\nTag:\n\nAI Assistant\n\nTitle:\n\nAsk AlumniIQ\n\nDescription:\n\nReceive intelligent answers using OpenAI Assistant API and alumni knowledge.\n\n---\n\nCard 2\n\nVideo:\n\nhttps://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_38xzZboKViGWJOttwIXH07lWA1P/hf_20260324_151826_c7218672-6e92-402c-9e45-f1e0f454bdc4.mp4\n\nTag:\n\nAnalytics\n\nTitle:\n\nCareer Intelligence Dashboard\n\nDescription:\n\nVisualize skills, industries, countries, and employers through interactive analytics.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 6 \342\200\224 ALUMNI EXPLORER SHOWCASE\n\nLarge product mockup.\n\nHeadline:\n\nExplore Thousands of Alumni Profiles\n\nFeatures:\n\n\342\234\223 Company Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Country Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Industry Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Skill Filters\n\n\342\234\223 Advanced Search\n\nDisplay realistic alumni cards.\n\nCard fields:\n\n* Name\n* Position\n* Company\n* Country\n* Education\n* Skills\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 7 \342\200\224 CAREER INSIGHTS SHOWCASE\n\nInteractive dashboard preview.\n\nHeadline:\n\nUnderstand Career Trends at Scale\n\nWidgets:\n\nTop Industries\n\nTop Countries\n\nTop Employers\n\nTop Skills\n\nCareer Growth Trends\n\nAnimated counters.\n\nGlass dashboard design.\n\n---\n\n# SECTION 8 \342\200\224 PLATFORM PREVIEW\n\nSplit-screen layout.\n\nLeft:\n\nAI Assistant\n\nRight:\n\nCareer Dashboard\n\nHeadline:\n\nOne Platform.\nUnlimited Alumni Intelligence.\n\nButtons:\n\nGet Started\n\nLogin\n\n---\n\n# LOGIN PAGE\n\nUse same design language as landing page.\n\nBackground:\n\nUse Hero Video\n\nDark overlay:\n\nbg-black/60\n\nCentered liquid-glass card.\n\nTitle:\n\nWelcome Back\n\nSubtitle:\n\nAccess the Alumni Career Intelligence Platform\n\nFields:\n\nEmail\n\nPassword\n\nRemember Me\n\nForgot Password\n\nButtons:\n\nSign In\n\nContinue with Google\n\nContinue with Microsoft\n\nDesktop Right Side:\n\nAnimated feature cards:\n\nAI Assistant\n\nAlumni Explorer\n\nCareer Insights\n\nSmooth floating animations.\n\n---\n\n# REGISTER PAGE\n\nFields:\n\nFull Name\n\nEmail\n\nUniversity\n\nPassword\n\nConfirm Password\n\nButton:\n\nCreate Account\n\nSocial Login:\n\nGoogle\n\nMicrosoft\n\n---\n\n# DASHBOARD\n\nModern SaaS dashboard.\n\nWelcome section.\n\nStatistics cards:\n\nTotal Alumni\n\nCompanies\n\nCountries\n\nIndustries\n\nSuggested Questions:\n\n* Which alumni work in Google?\n* Show alumni in Germany.\n* Top AI professionals.\n* Most common alumni skills.\n\nQuick Actions:\n\nAsk AI\n\nExplore Alumni\n\nView Insights\n\n---\n\n# AI ASSISTANT\n\nInspired by ChatGPT + Claude.\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Streaming Responses\n* Markdown Rendering\n* Code Blocks\n* Copy Response\n* Typing Animation\n* Suggested Prompts\n* Conversation History\n* Source References\n\nLayout:\n\nSidebar\n\nChat Area\n\nPrompt Input\n\n---\n\n# ALUMNI EXPLORER\n\nSearch\n\nFilter\n\nSort\n\nPagination\n\nGrid/List Toggle\n\nAlumni Card:\n\nPhoto\n\nName\n\nPosition\n\nCompany\n\nCountry\n\nEducation\n\nSkills\n\nLinkedIn Button\n\nProfile Modal\n\n---\n\n# CAREER INSIGHTS\n\nInteractive Charts.\n\nUse Recharts.\n\nShow:\n\nTop Skills\n\nTop Industries\n\nTop Countries\n\nTop Companies\n\nCareer Progression Trends\n\nAnimated Loading States.\n\n---\n\n# SIDEBAR\n\nInspired by Linear.\n\nSections:\n\nDashboard\n\nAI Assistant\n\nAlumni Explorer\n\nCareer Insights\n\nProfile\n\nSettings\n\nLogout\n\nCollapsible.\n\nMobile Drawer.\n\n---\n\n# STATE MANAGEMENT\n\nUse Zustand.\n\nStores:\n\nauthStore\n\nchatStore\n\nalumniStore\n\nanalyticsStore\n\nthemeStore\n\n---\n\n# API SERVICES\n\n/services\n\nauthService.ts\n\nassistantService.ts\n\nalumniService.ts\n\nanalyticsService.ts\n\n---\n\n# BACKEND STRUCTURE\n\nbackend/\n\napp/\n\napi/\n\nauth/\n\nassistant/\n\nalumni/\n\nanalytics/\n\nmodels/\n\nservices/\n\nconfig/\n\nutils/\n\nDatabase Models:\n\nUser\n\nAlumni\n\nCompany\n\nCountry\n\nIndustry\n\nChatHistory\n\n---\n\n# API ENDPOINTS\n\nPOST /api/auth/login\n\nPOST /api/auth/register\n\nPOST /api/auth/logout\n\nGET /api/alumni\n\nGET /api/alumni/search\n\nGET /api/alumni/:id\n\nGET /api/analytics\n\nPOST /api/assistant/chat\n\nGET /api/chat/history\n\n---\n\n# AI INTEGRATION\n\nOpenAI Assistant API\n\nCapabilities:\n\n* Alumni Search\n* Career Discovery\n* Industry Analysis\n* Skill Insights\n* Career Recommendations\n\nSupport:\n\nStreaming Responses\n\nConversation Memory\n\nSource Citations\n\n---\n\n# CODE QUALITY\n\nRequirements:\n\n* TypeScript Strict Mode\n* Reusable Components\n* SOLID Principles\n* Clean Architecture\n* Responsive Design\n* Accessibility Support\n* Loading Skeletons\n* Empty States\n* Error Boundaries\n* Production Ready\n\nGenerate the complete application including:\n\n* Folder Structure\n* Frontend\n* Backend\n* Authentication\n* Landing Page\n* Login/Register\n* Dashboard\n* AI Assistant\n* Alumni Explorer\n* Career Insights\n* API Layer\n* Zustand Stores\n* Responsive Design\n* OpenAI Integration\n* Flask Integration\n* Modern SaaS UI\n* All Components\n* All Pages\n* Production-Ready Architecture\n"
    }
  }
}
