  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Defining the AlumniIQ Platform**\n\nI\'m now zeroing in on defining AlumniIQ, a SaaS platform. The initial stage involves sketching out the core tech stack: React 19 with TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Lucide React, and Framer Motion for the frontend, while Python Flask, SQLAlchemy, and Flask Blue will drive the backend. These initial considerations are guiding the platform\'s foundation.\n\n\n**Adapting Tech Stack Preferences**\n\nI\'ve hit a snag with the initial tech stack. The environment constraints demand Node.js, so I\'m pivoting. Python/Flask is out, and I\'m now planning a Node.js (Express) backend, keeping Vite for the frontend. The challenge is translating my original Flask ideas, but the Express option aligns with the specifications. I need to make sure the JWT Auth works, and that I\'m able to use the OpenAI Assistant API. I also will use prints, and PostgreSQL.\n\n\n**Refining Visual Design Preferences**\n\nI\'m now zeroing in on the aesthetic design. The ultra-premium, dark-mode-first approach is key, incorporating glassmorphism and liquid glass elements. I\'ll need to nail the landing page with specific videos and Framer Motion effects. The background will be #000000, and Instrument Serif and Inter are the primary fonts. I\'m focusing on these elements to create a distinctive visual experience.\n\n\n**Planning the Backend Mock**\n\nI\'m now considering mocking the backend or using the Gemini API. The prompt references API keys, so I\'m thinking of using `process.env.GEMINI_API_KEY`. I\'m starting by setting up the React + Vite SPA structure and an Express server. Next, I\'ll install packages like Framer Motion, React Router, and Zustand. Then I will add shadcn/ui or custom liquid glass components, and after that, I\'ll build out the landing page, auth pages, protected layout, dashboard, AI Assistant, Alumni Explorer, and Career Insights, wiring up Zustand with a mock Express API.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 9
      nanos: 156359480
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
